                   </li>
                 </ul>
                 <div class="cell-100 border padding-2 margin-5 ae-7">
                   <h5 class="text-gray margin-bottom-1 uppercase opacity-5 letter-spacing-1">EXAMPLE</h5>
                   <p class="tight normal opacity-5">"We will read more about [growth mindset] for our first essay of the semester, but essentially a person with a growth mindset believes they can learn (even when it's difficult) and that the key to learning is putting in effort. I will do my best to encourage a growth mindset in our class, and I hope you will do the same."</p>
                </div>
